Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.24,0:00:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳等著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.40,0:00:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去找救兵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.65,0:00:17.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離昨晚的位置\N應該不會離太遠才對
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.68,0:00:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡跟埃爾斯汀真讓人擔心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.56,0:00:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我才沒有擔心她咧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.96,0:00:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.83,0:00:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.46,0:00:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎，愛莉卡她…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.93,0:00:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.17,0:00:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想沒什麼大不了的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.30,0:00:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是那個螞蟻\N遲早會自己冒出來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.81,0:00:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過\N只是單純遇難的話倒是還好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.62,0:00:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你介意的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.99,0:00:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一起參與搜索吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.35,0:00:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.22,0:00:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.93,0:01:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我有一樣東西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.66,0:01:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想派你藉這個機會去調查看看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.30,0:01:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十二王戰爭之前的遺跡是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.38,0:01:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願妳平安啦，可愛的姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.61,0:01:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會在星星的世界\N祈求妳的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.05,0:01:28.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螞蟻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.69,0:01:33.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.49,0:01:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不識相
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.36,0:01:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凱特斯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.70,0:01:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過·來·吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.91,0:01:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奴獸？是黑團？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.11,0:01:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，是黑谷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.13,0:02:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願你平安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.83,0:02:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也要在\N星星的世界獲得幸福喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.55,0:02:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找到夢想了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.86,0:02:42.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內心悸動無法平息
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.80,0:02:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寶物誕生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.37,0:03:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滿盈內心 開始散放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.55,0:03:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何會如此不安呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.25,0:03:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法控制的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.89,0:03:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓人不禁落淚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.30,0:03:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有朝一日一定會抵達
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.34,0:03:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算中途受挫也不放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.54,0:03:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼓起勇氣向前邁進
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.58,0:03:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能踏出小小的一步 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.19,0:03:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是嶄新的我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.80,0:03:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第10話 那是少女的一件大事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.44,0:03:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天在這裡過夜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.41,0:04:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千繪姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.78,0:04:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來接妳們了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.44,0:04:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健行考試終止
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.95,0:04:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.91,0:04:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡那一組遇難了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.88,0:04:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛是找到埃爾斯了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.12,0:04:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是愛莉卡…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.56,0:04:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依然行蹤不明
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.39,0:04:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛莉卡她…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.36,0:04:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.26,0:04:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以大夥一邊尋找
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.87,0:04:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一邊將其他學生帶回來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.07,0:04:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳冷靜點聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.41,0:04:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,協助搜索的王少校也失聯了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.57,0:05:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螞蟻，妳振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.75,0:05:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加爾德羅貝的學生？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.22,0:05:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一艘\N應該是來找學生的小船
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.42,0:05:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動作快
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.89,0:05:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯曼，不用監視了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.09,0:05:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟戴因交換吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.27,0:05:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.51,0:05:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳真的順利帶她回來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.44,0:05:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她很聰明
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.65,0:05:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之她極力忍著\N想衝出去的衝動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.35,0:05:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.25,0:05:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在發什麼呆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.89,0:05:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點找出愛莉卡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.96,0:05:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們也去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.49,0:06:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點動作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.19,0:06:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下，您如此擔心\N愛莉卡的安危嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.40,0:06:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我討厭她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.73,0:06:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是她要是出事了我會很頭痛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.84,0:06:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師，埃爾斯她…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.15,0:06:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的，不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.45,0:06:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.32,0:06:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.49,0:06:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下只要愛莉卡沒事的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.96,0:06:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.83,0:06:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我給她注射活性化劑之後
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.77,0:06:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毒素毫無問題地分解了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.67,0:06:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，這樣子的話\N她們兩個人應該也試過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.58,0:06:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是，不知為何沒有生效
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.88,0:06:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學園長
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.38,0:06:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡記錄有高次物質化反應
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.69,0:07:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是舞鬥服的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.22,0:07:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是王少校失聯的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.76,0:07:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.50,0:07:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓我去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.97,0:07:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.07,0:07:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親他…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.51,0:07:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道妳很難過
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.91,0:07:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是現在請妳忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.88,0:07:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.12,0:07:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一定會找到他的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.49,0:07:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.14,0:07:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡，變冷了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.78,0:08:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不能生火讓人發現我們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.43,0:08:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.19,0:08:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.40,0:08:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要丟下…我一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.90,0:08:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螞蟻…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.21,0:08:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷…喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.69,0:08:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.72,0:09:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別鬧了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.05,0:09:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子跟妮娜一樣大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.96,0:09:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊張什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.99,0:09:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.73,0:09:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體還這麼瘦小
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.63,0:09:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以這麼…纖細的身體…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.61,0:09:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我好不容易找到的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.38,0:09:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就算是亂來也好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.21,0:09:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要拼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.64,0:10:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改造人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.11,0:10:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且附近海岸上留有小船的殘骸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.08,0:10:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.35,0:10:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.02,0:10:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說，那個遺跡是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.99,0:10:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是在移民曆很早期時\N建造的研究設施
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.06,0:10:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾年前曾經調查過裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.70,0:10:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是什麼都沒發現
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.20,0:10:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.20,0:10:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的，為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.47,0:10:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管他怎樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.84,0:10:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之我們快點去找
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.28,0:10:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學園長
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.18,0:10:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝各位提供情報
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.38,0:10:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的事情愛瑞斯會處理
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.89,0:10:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閣下，請批准我的部隊出動
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.69,0:10:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪之！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.93,0:11:00.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.89,0:11:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼妳不行動？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.00,0:11:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請也讓我去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.00,0:11:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果只是搜索還沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.90,0:11:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是加爾德羅貝不能在\N沒有審議會批准的情況下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.47,0:11:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,介入我國的利害關係
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.71,0:11:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.81,0:11:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.05,0:11:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有三名以上的\N審議委員同意的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.75,0:11:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以認同臨時動議
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.49,0:11:27.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.59,0:11:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.49,0:11:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.22,0:11:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殿下…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.83,0:11:37.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜，妳這女孩真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.90,0:11:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時候也差不多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.47,0:11:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.03,0:11:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟他是我重要的左右手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.07,0:11:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.99,0:12:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.29,0:12:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像…很溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.29,0:12:08.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有種…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.75,0:12:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.75,0:12:33.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊～～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.95,0:12:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢…慢著，螞蟻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.22,0:12:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳先遮一下啦笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.59,0:12:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遮住妳那個飛機場胸部
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.83,0:12:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.50,0:12:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很瞭解妳的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.07,0:12:49.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過請妳稍微手下留情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.44,0:12:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.87,0:12:53.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.57,0:12:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳快點把衣服穿上啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.67,0:12:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿好之後我再解釋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.15,0:13:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.98,0:13:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的什麼都沒做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.99,0:13:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伽爾，還沒好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.56,0:13:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉德，你很沒耐性耶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.96,0:13:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就當作上了一艘大船
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.97,0:13:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我表現吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.67,0:13:27.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後妳就一個人？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.57,0:13:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是，太亂來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.74,0:13:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.58,0:13:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不這樣做，埃爾斯她…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.24,0:13:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃爾斯她有沒有事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.51,0:13:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想她應該已經被找到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.42,0:13:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.45,0:13:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們動作還是快點的好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.72,0:13:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個，原則上謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.22,0:13:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.06,0:13:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我謝爾蓋就好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.93,0:13:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我可不會因為你看光我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.14,0:13:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就跟你稱兄道弟的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.87,0:14:02.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼，妳會不會想太多
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.27,0:14:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳這隻螞蟻還早個10年呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.41,0:14:06.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.31,0:14:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.85,0:14:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早餐之前呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.72,0:14:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以，為了報答那個人的期望
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.43,0:14:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會成為出色的乙HiME
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.70,0:14:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然有人這麼好事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.50,0:14:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.83,0:14:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.80,0:14:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳真好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.04,0:14:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是這麼開心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.84,0:14:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼，你不開心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.71,0:14:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不可能一直開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.18,0:14:40.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.01,0:14:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是想當軍人才從軍的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.68,0:14:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理想跟現實
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.65,0:14:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,常常是兩回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.19,0:14:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼突然？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.04,0:15:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們是什麼人？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.84,0:15:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑谷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.31,0:15:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不屬於任何國家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.18,0:15:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂泊的民族
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.78,0:15:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信奉移民曆之前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.21,0:15:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球時代科學的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.98,0:15:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.29,0:15:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.69,0:15:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭領
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.06,0:15:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砍了他們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.76,0:15:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.27,0:15:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉呀？唉呀呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.94,0:15:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可愛的姑娘，妳還活著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.20,0:15:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,運氣真好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.21,0:15:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.12,0:15:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想在我美麗的\N愛瑞斯領地內進行破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.56,0:16:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物質化
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.09,0:16:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小遙，還沒認證啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.63,0:16:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.03,0:16:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁現在，動手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.58,0:16:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜留姊，妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.91,0:16:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.85,0:16:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝爾蓋，你還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.98,0:16:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.82,0:16:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜，妳救了我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.52,0:16:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請就此罷手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.29,0:16:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏樹·庫魯格
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.43,0:16:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑谷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.60,0:16:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潛入這種地方是看上了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.65,0:16:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加爾德羅貝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.25,0:17:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏匿科學技術
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.19,0:17:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扭曲世界的元兇嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.02,0:17:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憑妳們能攔住我們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.56,0:17:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴，你們這些罪犯…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.20,0:17:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小遙，妳還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.06,0:17:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說過\N不要在別人面前叫我小遙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.77,0:17:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認證吧，快點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.47,0:17:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙·阿米特吉\N威猛的珠洲的黃玉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.37,0:17:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以吾之名解放汝之力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.68,0:17:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重新來過
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.78,0:17:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物～質化
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.79,0:17:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的罪犯們，覺悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.37,0:17:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈米機械開始活性化
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.84,0:17:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到加速界限為止300秒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.07,0:17:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆彈粉碎球
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.41,0:18:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,徒手接下那招？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.48,0:18:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了我等的宿願
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.65,0:18:08.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乙HiME們啊，受死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.30,0:18:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個由我們黑團接收了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.30,0:18:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碧女士
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.84,0:18:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史密斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.71,0:18:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.68,0:18:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快追
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.88,0:18:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜留
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.08,0:18:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳們的對手是我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.92,0:18:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現身吧，鋼之牙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.99,0:18:42.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愕天王
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.27,0:18:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愕天王？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.44,0:19:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不怕我和愕天王的力量\N就儘管過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.55,0:19:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過就是隻區區奴獸罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.85,0:19:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天真
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.45,0:19:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小遙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.67,0:19:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.10,0:19:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺有本事的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.67,0:19:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.94,0:19:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼強的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.37,0:19:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要用在\N守護扭曲的世界上？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.34,0:19:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還用說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.04,0:19:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是為了我重視的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.58,0:19:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就以死來貫徹意志吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.72,0:19:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愕天王，吶喊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.81,0:20:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此為止了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.98,0:20:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這場比劃先保留下了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.12,0:20:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊，妳給我記住
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.93,0:20:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.84,0:20:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.44,0:20:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.41,0:20:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.85,0:20:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考試還是要重新來過
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.48,0:20:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家雖然抱怨連連
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.62,0:20:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我卻覺得這樣正好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.90,0:21:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得發生很多事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.70,0:21:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多多少少怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.47,0:21:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你別太介意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.47,0:21:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會為了成為\N出色的乙HiME而努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.44,0:21:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以叔叔\N請你耐心等到那時候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.92,0:21:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，雖然不捨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.02,0:21:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我也照計劃回國去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.82,0:21:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些女人好像\N又偷偷要做些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.16,0:21:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.03,0:21:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的\N都是些笨蛋真讓人頭痛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.86,0:21:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知道就讓你事先把哥哥的\N老婆和小鬼們處理掉就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.81,0:21:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殿下，您在計劃些什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.91,0:21:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是指黑團嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.61,0:21:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.61,0:21:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認為呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.88,0:21:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.38,0:22:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也有事情瞞著我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.99,0:22:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.59,0:22:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以背叛我喔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.29,0:22:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.39,0:22:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇氣會實現願望 Do your best
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.43,0:22:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別認輸 向前邁進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.21,0:22:37.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只等著我的故事 現在開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.25,0:22:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其逃避 不如挺身面對更好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.00,0:22:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是少女的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.13,0:22:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很努力唷\N就算內心突然感到寂寞的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.64,0:22:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要以笑容面對
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.64,0:23:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼NO NO NO 你的世界裡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.65,0:23:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定有快樂的未來 我想守護你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.89,0:23:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.02,0:23:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清澄的心意 比寶石更耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.46,0:23:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿出自信向前邁進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.44,0:23:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別認輸 向前邁進吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.78,0:23:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太賊了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.62,0:23:43.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然只有妳用了愕天王\N（生日☆快樂）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.25,0:23:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.22,0:23:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不也有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.26,0:23:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靜…靜留？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.42,0:23:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是杜藍
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.49,0:23:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，妳舔哪裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.40,0:23:54.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕的嬌嫣的紫水晶…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.50,0:00:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.50,0:00:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,


